Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga mugunta da fushin jam'iyyar Democrat
"Zabe na ga Alkali Kavanaugh ya nuna rashin amincewa da mummunan aiki da kuma mummunan aiki na jam'iyyar Democrat", in ji Trump a wani taron da aka yi a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya fuskanci mummunan hali da fushin jam'iyyar Democrat a lokacin da yake neman kujerar shugaban kasa.
Kavanaugh ya shaida a gaban majalisa a ranar Alhamis inda ya yi tir da zargin Christine Blasey Ford cewa ya yi lalata da ita shekaru da dama da suka gabata lokacin da suke matasa.
Ford ta yi shaida a lokacin da ake tuhumar ta.
