Ya shaida wa magoya bayansa a West Virginia cewa, kuri'ar da ya kada ta tabbatar da Alkalin Kavanaugh, ita ce tabbatar da daya daga cikin manyan masu shari'a na zamaninmu, lauya mai kyakkyawan aiki ga jama'a.
Shugaban ya yi magana a kan Kavanaugh a lokacin da ya yi magana game da muhimmancin 'yan Republican su shiga zaben tsakiyar zangon.
Makonni biyar kafin wani babban zabe a rayuwarmu.
Ban yi takara ba, amma ina kan tafiya, "in ji shi.
"Saboda haka, ina fafatawa a ko'ina don manyan 'yan takara".
Trump ya ce 'yan Democrat sun zabi 'resistance and obstruction'.
