Shugaban Mexico AMLO ya yi alkawarin ba zai yi amfani da sojoji kan fararen hula ba
A ranar tunawa da shekaru 50 da kisan gillar da aka yi wa daliban, sabon shugaban kasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba amfani da karfin soja a kan fararen hula ba.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba amfani da sojoji ba don zaluntar mutanen Mexico.
A lokacin da 'yan makaranta masu son siyasa suke yaɗuwa a Latin Amirka, a ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojoji suka fara harbi mutane da suke zanga-zanga a wani fili kuma mutane 300 suka mutu.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin tallafawa matasa 'yan Mexico ta hanyar biyan kudaden tallafi na wata-wata ga masu karatu da kuma bude wasu jami'o'in gwamnati kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin ilimi suna jawo matasa zuwa ƙungiyoyin 'yan daba.
Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take baiwa AI
A cewar mai saka jari kuma masanin ilimin kere kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple, China tana kara aiki a fannin ilimin kere kere (AI) kuma Amurka ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa a fannin binciken.
Wannan magana ta zo ne bayan da sassan gwamnatin Amurka suka yi sanarwa game da AI, duk da cewa Amurka gabaɗaya ba ta da wata dabara ta AI.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta gabatar da wani shiri na zama kasa ta farko a fannin kirkire-kirkire na AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"A ninka kasafin kudin da muke kashewa wajen gudanar da bincike kan AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda sauran kasashen duniya sun fi Amurka nesa, kuma muna neman wani ci gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
Lee ya bayyana a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon cewa ninka kudaden zai ninka yiwuwar cewa babbar sabuwar fasaha ta wucin gadi za ta kasance a Amurka.
Lee, wanda ya wallafa littafinsa mai suna AI Superpower: China, Silicon Valley da kuma New World Order a wannan watan daga Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne babban darektan kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a kasar Sin, Face++.
A Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya zarce mafi kyawun ɗan wasan Amurka a wasan Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama babban jami'in bincike na Microsoft kuma shugaban kamfanin Google na China.
