Mene ne bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma me ya yi don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, bikin kiɗan na shekara-shekara na Global Citizen Festival na New York City, wanda ke ba da jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa don kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai maraba da dubban mutane da za su taru a Central Park don jin daɗin ba kawai masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron, wanda shine kawo ƙarshen talauci ta 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen wanda aka ƙaddamar a cikin 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty, ƙungiyar ƙasa da ƙasa don tallafawa ƙarshen talauci ta hanyar haɓaka yawan mutanen da ke aiki don magance ta.
Don samun tikitin zuwa taron kyauta (sai dai idan ba ku so ku biya kuɗin VIP), masu halarta dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka ko ayyuka kamar aikin sa kai, imel zuwa shugaban duniya, kiran waya, ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da manufarsu ta kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen ta kasance shekaru 12 kafin ta cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da kyauta ta kyauta ta hanyar lallashe su su nemi aiki ne, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" - mutane suna jin cewa ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kan layi ko aika tweet, zasu kawo canji?
Global Citizen ya ce tun daga shekarar 2011 ya samu sama da ayyuka miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa, suna kokarin cimma wasu manufofi.
Ya ce waɗannan ayyuka sun sa shugabannin duniya suka sanar da alkawura da kuma matakan da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane fiye da biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta sanar da alkawura 390 da sanarwar da ta samo asali daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka biya ko aka ba da kuɗi.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka bayar sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Babban alƙawarin da aka yi ya haɗa da Project of Power of Nutrition, haɗin gwiwar masu saka hannun jari da masu haɓaka Burtaniya waɗanda suka yi alkawarin taimaka wa yara su haɓaka zuwa cikakkiyar damarsu, suna alƙawarin ba Rwanda dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa wajen kawo ƙarshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a yankin bayan karɓar tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasa da na Global Citizens kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci a cikin rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin sanarwa a tarihi, Ambassador na Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman ya fada wa taron a wani wasan kwaikwayo a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki mataki sama da 5,000 a kasar don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da bayar da tallafin shirin samar da abinci mai gina jiki wanda zai shafi mata da yara miliyan biyar.
A cikin amsa ga daya daga cikin tambayoyin da aka fi yi a shafin yanar gizonmu, "Me ya sa kake tsammanin za mu iya kawo ƙarshen talauci?"
