Wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web yana shirin fara sabuwar intanet da za ta wuce Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta yanar gizo, ya fara wani kamfani da zai yi gasa da Facebook da Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ke gina akan dandamali na Open Source na Berners-Lee wanda ake kira Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda za su iya samun damar bayanai.
A wata hira da Fast Company Berners-Lee yayi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt shine "mulkin duniya".
