A Jamus sabon jirgin yaki sake saita
An amince da sabon jirgin ruwan sojin ruwa na Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War amma ba za a samu damar yin amfani da shi ba a kalla shekara guda saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma dusar ƙanƙara a gabar teku, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
A cewar jaridar Die Zeit, mai magana da yawun rundunar soji, an dage ƙaddamar da jirgin ruwa mai suna Rheinland-Pfalz, sabuwar jirgin ruwa mai suna Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin 2019.
An shirya jirgin zai shiga cikin rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsaloli masu yawa bayan an kawo shi sun haifar da damuwa game da makomar wannan babban aikin.
Za a maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na Bremen da ke tsufa da jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg, wanda rundunar ta umarci a 2007.
A bayyane yake cewa za su kasance suna da makamai masu ƙarfi, da wasu makamai masu linzami da na ruwa da kuma wasu fasahohin da ba a sani ba kamar radar da infrared da kuma sauti.
Sauran muhimman fasalulluka sun hada da tsawon lokacin kulawa  ya kamata a iya tura sabbin jiragen ruwa na tsawon shekaru biyu a wajen tashar jiragen ruwa ta gida.
Amma, ci gaba da jinkiri yana nufin cewa manyan jiragen ruwa  da aka ce za su ba Jamus damar tura sojoji zuwa ƙasashen waje  za su zama tsofaffi kafin a soma aiki, in ji Die Zeit.
An yi ta buga labarin sanannen jirgin ruwan F125 a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta hana shi aiki kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa kamfanin Blohm & Voss da ke Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta mayar da jirgin sama ga masana'antun bayan an ba da shi.
Ba a san komai ba game da dalilan da suka sa aka dawo da su, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci manyan kurakurai da yawa na "kayan aiki da kuma lalacewar kayan aiki" wanda zai sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a lokacin da aka tura shi.
Rashin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci, saboda jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg zai yi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120,  rabin ma'aikatan da ake buƙata a kan jirgin ruwa na Bremen.
Har ila yau, an nuna cewa jirgin yana da nauyin nauyi, wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya rage ikon da Navy ke da shi don ƙara sababbin sababbin abubuwa.
An yi imani cewa jirgin ruwa mai nauyin tan 7,000 na Rheinland-Pfal zai ninka nauyin jirage iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga gazawar kayan aikin, farashin aikin , gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin, shine matsalar.
An ce farashin ya ƙaru daga biliyan biyu da ɗari biyu zuwa biliyan uku da ɗari uku.
Matsalolin da ke tattare da sababbin jiragen ruwa sun zama sananne musamman a cikin hasken da aka yi a kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus ya tabbatar da cewa sojojin ruwa na da 'ƙarancin jiragen ruwa masu amfani.
Wannan jami'in ya bayyana cewa matsalolin sun ci gaba da kasancewa saboda an cire tsofaffin jiragen ruwa daga aiki amma ba a ba da wani abu ba.
