Brexit: Birtaniya za ta ci gaba da nadamar asarar da ta yi wa masana'antun motoci
Birtaniya za ta ci gaba da nadamar rasa matsayin da take da shi na jagorar kera motoci bayan Brexit, in ji sakataren harkokin kasuwanci Greg Clark.
Ya kara da cewa "abin damuwa ne" cewa kamfanin kera motoci na Toyota UK ya shaida wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta bar EU ba tare da yarjejeniya ba, za ta dakatar da samar da kayayyaki a tashar Burnaston da ke kusa da Derby.
"Dangane da wannan, akwai bukatar yarjejeniya", Clark ya ce.
Kamfanin kera motoci na Japan ya ce jinkirin da ake samu a kan iyakar kasar zai iya jawo asarar ayyukan yi idan ba a cimma yarjejeniyar ficewa daga EU ba.
A cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kusan motoci 150,000 aka kera a tashar Burnston, inda ake kera motocin Toyota Auris da Avensis, kuma kashi 90% na motocin an fitar da su zuwa sauran ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai.
"A ganina idan Birtaniya ta fice daga EU a karshen watan Maris, za mu fuskanci cikas a masana'antarmu", in ji Marvin Cooke, shugaban kamfanin Toyota a Burnston.
Sauran kamfanonin kera motoci, ciki har da motocin Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover a Burtaniya suna yada fargabar barin EU ba tare da yarjejeniya ba game da yadda cinikin kan iyaka ke gudana.
Alal misali, kamfanin BMW ya ce zai rufe masana'antar kera motocin Mini da ke Oxford wata daya bayan Brexit.
Babban abin damuwa ya shafi abin da masana'antun ke nunawa a matsayin haɗarin sarkar samarwa a cikin yanayin Brexit ba tare da yarjejeniya ba.
Toyota ta samar da layin aiki akan isar da kayayyaki akan lokaci, tare da sassan da aka kawo daga masu samar da kayayyaki a Burtaniya da EU don motocin da aka kera akan buƙata cikin minti 37.
Idan Birtaniya ta bar EU a ranar 29 ga watan Maris ba tare da yarjejeniya ba, za a iya samun rikice-rikice a kan iyakar, wanda masana'antu suka ce zai haifar da jinkiri da karancin kayayyakin gyara.
Kamfanin Toyota ya ce ba zai yiwu kamfanin ya ajiye kayan aiki fiye da kwana ɗaya a Derbyshire ba, kuma hakan zai kawo ƙarshen samar da kayayyaki.
Mista Clark ya ce shirin Theresa May na farfado da dangantakarta da EU a nan gaba an daidaita shi sosai don kada a samu irin wannan sa ido a kan iyakoki.
"Muna bukatar yarjejeniya.Muna son samun mafi kyawun yarjejeniya da za ta ba mu damar, kamar yadda na ce, ba kawai nasararmu ta yanzu ba amma kuma mu yi amfani da wannan damar",in ji shi a shirin BBC Radio 4's Today.
Gaskiya ba kawai daga Toyota ba amma daga wasu masana'antun masana'antu shine cewa dole ne mu kasance da cikakken ikon ci gaba da abin da ke da matukar nasara a cikin jerin jerin kayan aiki.
Toyota ba ta iya cewa tsawon lokacin da za a dakatar da samarwa ba, amma ta yi gargadin cewa a cikin dogon lokaci, ƙarin farashin zai rage gasa a masana'antar kuma a ƙarshe ya kasance a kan farashin ayyukan yi.
Peter Tsouvallaris, wanda ya yi aiki a Burnaston tsawon shekaru 24 kuma shugaban ma'aikata ne a ma'aikatar, ya ce 'yan kungiya sun kara damuwa: "Na samu labari cewa idan aka rasa wadannan wuraren aiki, ba za su sake dawowa ba.
Mai magana da yawun gwamnatin ya ce: Mun kafa tsari mai kyau da kuma tabbatacce na dangantakarmu ta gaba da EU.
An sake jinkirta ganawar Trump da Rosenstein, in ji fadar White House
Za a iya jinkirta ganawar Donald Trump da lauya janar Rod Rosenstein har zuwa mako guda, saboda ci gaba da takarar babban alkalin kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, fadar White House ta sanar a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin kwararren mai ba da shawara Robert Mueller wanda ke binciken yadda aka yi amfani da Rasha wajen jefa kuri'a, da alakar da ke tsakanin magoya bayan Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban kasa shiga shari'a.
Ko da Trump ya kori mataimakin babban jami'in, kuma hakan ya shafi 'yancin Mueller, an yi watanni ana ta jita-jita a Washington.
A farkon wannan watan jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna batun sanya kyamarar daukar hoto don rikodin tattaunawa da Trump da kuma yiwuwar tsige shugaban ta hanyar Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan rahoton.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya bayyana a fadar White House yana mai cewa zai yi murabus.
Maimakon haka, an sanar da ganawa da Trump a ranar Alhamis, wanda a lokacin yana hedkwatar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce ba zai bar Rosenstein ba, amma sai aka jinkirta taron don kada ya yi karo da sauraron sauraron shari'ar da aka yi a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai, inda Kavanaugh da wata mata da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka shaida.
