Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma hukumomi sun ce ana sa ran adadin zai karu.
Saboda rashin sadarwa, jami'an tsaro ba su samu wani bayani ba daga gundumar Donggala, yankin da ke arewacin Palau, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
Bayan bala'in ya auku, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palau.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da garin Palu da kuma yankin Donggala, a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke a ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi kuma an kiyasta yawan jama'arta a cikin 2017 ya kai 379,800.
A lokacin da aka yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafa birnin, sai aka yi wata girgizar ƙasa da tsunami.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, yawan mutanen da ke cikin yankin ya kai 299,200.
Babban bangaren tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi shine kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
A cikin lardin akwai ma'adinai masu yawa na nickel, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i a ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi tsunami a birnin Pala da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami da ya auku a Donggale ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa yankin Donggala na yamma a shekarar 1996 inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Fasifik kuma ana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga jerin manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ta haddasa tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a lardin Aceh.
2005: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta haddasa tsunami da ya auku a gabar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta auku kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka rasa rayukansu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani ƙaramin girgizar ƙasa ya afku a yankin Pidie Jaya da ke lardin Aceh, ya haddasa ɓarna da firgici, saboda yana tunatar da mutane game da mummunar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da ta auku a shekara ta 2004.
