An kama babban dan Sarah Palin a kan zargin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi ne bisa zargin cin zarafin mutum.
A cewar rahoton da 'yan sanda suka fitar a ranar Asabar, an kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga garin Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin aikata laifin tashin hankali a gida, da kuma hana bayar da rahoton tashin hankali a gida da kuma yin tsayayya da kama.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa wata budurwarsa ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta kai rahoton aikata laifuka, sai aka kwace wayar Palin.
An tura Palin zuwa gidan Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an tsare shi a kan bashin da ba a biya ba na dala 500, in ji KTUU.
A cewar wani rahoto da kafar yada labarai ta wallafa, ya bayyana a gaban kotu ranar Asabar inda ya bayyana cewa yana jin "ba shi da laifi" lokacin da aka tambaye shi ko ya yi magana.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin cewa zai iya fuskantar hukuncin daurin shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake yankewa hukuncin daurin kwana daya a gidan yari da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka kai Palin kotu ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an tuhume shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa Sarah Palin ce ta kai rahoton harin da ake zargin 'yan sanda da yi.
Yanzu haka dai ana shari'ar ne a kotun tsaron sojin kasar Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifukan tashin hankali a cikin gida, da karya dokar bayar da rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma mallakar makami a cikin mahallin da ke da alaƙa da miyagun ƙwayoyi dangane da lamarin.
Ya ce ya bugi budurwarsa a fuska.
A shekarar 2016, kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji sun soki Sarah Palin saboda ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da matsalar damuwa ta bayan-tashin hankali da aikin danta a Iraki ya haifar.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia: Daruruwan Mutane Sun Mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan da wata girgizar kasa ta afku a tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a.
Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta haddasa tsunami kuma ta halaka dubban gidaje.
Lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa sun lalace kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a kwanaki masu zuwa.
An yi wata girgizar ƙasa a tsibirin Sulawesi da ke arewa maso gabashin Jakarta, babban birnin ƙasar Indonesia.
Wasu bidiyo sun bayyana a shafukan sada zumunta da ke nuna lokacin bala'in.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don su halarci wani biki a bakin teku a birnin Palu, bayan da tsunami ya auko bakin tekun.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yankewa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci hukuncin kisa
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi a yankewa Sayfullah Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York da ya kashe mutane takwas. Wannan hukunci ne na musamman da ba a yankewa wani laifi a jihar ba tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, an ce ya kai harin ne a wata hanyar hawa keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan a watan Oktoba ta hanyar amfani da wata motar haya da aka yi haya da ta yi amfani da ita wajen tarwatsa masu tafiya da keke.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni. Wannan shine yadda aka bayyana sharuddan da aka yanke don yanke hukuncin kisa a cikin takardar da kotu ta amince da shi a gundumar kudu ta New York.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, waɗannan adadi biyu za su iya sa a yi kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuffuka 22, ciki har da zargin kisan kai da ake amfani da shi wajen yin barazana, wanda ake amfani da shi a kotun tarayya don shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "tsari da shiri sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna mai bayyana yadda Saip ya aikata abin da ya munana, mai tsanani da kuma lalata.
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haddasa rauni, ciwo da asarar dangi da abokai Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernán Ferruchi, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Pagnucco, an ambata a cikin niyyar.
Wadanda aka kashe biyar daga cikin su 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da kotu ta yanke hukuncin kisa a gundumar New York ta kudu.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan wasu 'yan kasuwar miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar shekarar 2009.
A ƙarshe, an yi kisa a New York a shekara ta 1953 a kan hukuncin kisa na Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa a kan zargin su da yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka wuce.
An kashe Rosenberg da matarsa a kan kujera a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama kadan a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya ji daɗin abin da ya yi.
A cewar zargin, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa kallon bidiyon ISIL a wayar sa ne ya sa ya kai harin.
'Yan sanda sun kuma bayyana cewa ya nemi a saka tutar kungiyar IS a dakin jinya.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume guda 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin gwamnatin tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi takaicin matakin da masu gabatar da kara suka dauka.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar laifin da hukuncin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai kara tsawaita cutar da wadannan abubuwan suka haifar ga duk wanda suka shafa", in ji Patton.
A baya, lauyoyin Saipov sun nemi masu gabatar da kara da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
