Ƙungiyar 'yan wasa ta farko: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya zura kwallo biyu a raga a wasan Giants da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun gyara rashin nasarar da suka yi a gasar Premier ta ranar Juma'a da Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan ramuwar gayya a ranar Asabar a Dundee wanda ya ƙare 5-3.
Giants sun samu ci gaba da ci biyu a raga, tare da buga kwallo daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita a gida kafin Dwyer ya dawo da Giants.
Bayan haka, Francois Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa Dundee, inda kwallo biyu da Lukaku Lundwald Nielsen ya ci ya tabbatar da nasarar su.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da kungiyar kwallon kafa ta kasar ta Premier ta sha kashi a kakar bana a hannun Adam Keefe, inda suka doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a wasan da suka buga a Belfast ranar Juma'a.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu ke karawa a bana, kuma duk wasannin uku da suka gabata, 'yan wasan Giants ne suka yi nasara.
Dwyer ta fara cin kwallo a minti na hudu, a 3:35 na ranar, tare da taimakon Kendall McFaul, yayin da David Rutherford ya ba da gudummawa ga Beauvillier ta biyu minti hudu daga baya.
Da farko kashi na uku ya kasance mai ban tsoro lokacin da Sullivan ya dawo da gida a cikin wasa a 13:10 sannan Matt Marquardt ya shirya kwallo ga Cownie wanda ya daidaita a 15:16.
Dwyer ya sa Giants suka shiga cikin hutun farko na hutun farko, suna kan gaba, lokacin da ya zira kwallo ta biyu a daren a ƙarshen kashi na farko.
'Yan wasan gida sun sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaita burin da ya samu daga wasan gaba a cikin lokaci 27:37.
Aikin Cownie da Charles Corcoran tare ya taimaka wa Nielsen ya sauya jagorancin Dundee a karo na farko a wasan, kuma wannan dan wasan ya tabbatar da jagorancin tawagarsa a tsakiyar na karshe.
